flowchart TD
    A[PM opens /overview/pm] --> B[Browser loads projected task summaries from GET /tasks]
    B --> C[Browser loads canonical roster from GET /ai-agents]
    C --> D[Client resolves current owner into one PM bucket]
    D --> E{Bucket result}
    E -- No owner --> F[Place task in Unassigned]
    E -- Canonical role match --> G[Place task in Architect or Engineer or QA or SRE]
    E -- Hidden or unresolved mapping --> H[Place task in Needs routing attention]
    F --> I[Render grouped read-only sections]
    G --> I
    H --> I
    I --> J{Single bucket filter active?}
    J -- No --> K[Show non-empty sections in required order]
    J -- Yes --> L[Show only the selected bucket section]
    L --> M[Clear filter restores grouped overview]
    K --> N[Refresh reloads projection and moves reassigned tasks between buckets]
    M --> N
